Yes.

1038
01:18:05,579 --> 01:18:07,752
And you will be you again.

1039
01:18:09,950 --> 01:18:14,194
My boy, I understand your unhappiness.

1040
01:18:15,389 --> 01:18:17,266
I understand your pain.

1041
01:18:18,259 --> 01:18:20,865
And I can make it go away.

1042
01:18:23,030 --> 01:18:26,477
You will close your eyes and you will sleep.

1043
01:18:27,735 --> 01:18:30,215
And when you wake up,

1044
01:18:30,271 --> 01:18:32,444
you'll be just fine.

1045
01:18:43,584 --> 01:18:47,031
He is dead?

1046
01:18:47,755 --> 01:18:49,735
He's nothing but clay.

1047
01:18:50,925 --> 01:18:54,168
But we can all breathe life into him.

1048
01:18:56,597 --> 01:19:00,443
You see, that is the secret
that God is so jealous of.

1049
01:19:01,702 --> 01:19:03,079
The formula for life.

1050
01:19:03,871 --> 01:19:07,216
And I, me, Dr. Frankenstein,

1051
01:19:08,943 --> 01:19:10,388
discovered it,

1052
01:19:10,444 --> 01:19:12,048
and I will do it again.

1053
01:19:29,997 --> 01:19:32,603
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

1054
01:19:34,034 --> 01:19:35,445
(MACHINE BEEPING)

1055
01:19:38,506 --> 01:19:39,985
MONSTER: No!

1056
01:19:41,775 --> 01:19:43,982
I am!

1057
01:19:52,653 --> 01:19:53,927
(PANTING)

1058
01:19:56,357 --> 01:19:58,598
lam.

1059
01:19:59,026 --> 01:20:01,472
I am.

1060
01:20:01,962 --> 01:20:04,135
I am. I am.

1061
01:20:04,632 --> 01:20:08,102
I am.

1062
01:20:10,070 --> 01:20:11,310
You.

1063
01:20:12,106 --> 01:20:14,177
You made me.

1064
01:20:17,878 --> 01:20:22,850
You hate me.

1065
01:20:23,350 --> 01:20:24,488
No.

1066
01:20:30,257 --> 01:20:34,228
I'm alone.

1067
01:20:37,865 --> 01:20:42,678
I'm alone.

1068
01:20:45,272 --> 01:20:46,342
(GASPS)

1069
01:20:54,748 --> 01:20:56,591
(GROANING)

1070
01:21:04,058 --> 01:21:06,402
I'll decapitate him
and then incinerate his head.

1071
01:21:06,460 --> 01:21:07,768
- Get off.
- No.

1072
01:21:07,828 --> 01:21:08,863
- Move.
- I can't.

1073
01:21:08,929 --> 01:21:10,203
Don't be ridiculous.

1074
01:21:10,264 --> 01:21:11,368
(ELIZABETH GRUNTS)

1075
01:21:13,167 --> 01:21:14,305
(GURGLING)

1076
01:21:15,703 --> 01:21:17,546
(YELLING)

1077
01:21:19,206 --> 01:21:20,310
(GROANS)

1078
01:21:21,875 --> 01:21:23,684
No. Oh.

1079
01:21:24,979 --> 01:21:27,459
Oh, my God. Oh, no.

1080
01:21:29,083 --> 01:21:30,187
(MOANS)

1081
01:21:34,421 --> 01:21:36,025
(BIRDS CHIRPING)

1082
01:21:38,525 --> 01:21:39,629
(VICTOR SOBS)

1083
01:21:54,174 --> 01:21:56,154
(ELEVATOR WHIRRING)

1084
01:22:49,663 --> 01:22:55,477
<i>MONSTER: I shall collect my funeral pile
and consume to ashes this miserable frame.</i>

1085
01:22:57,037 --> 01:23:01,349
<i>That its remains may afford no light
to any curious and unhallowed wretch</i>

1086
01:23:01,408 --> 01:23:03,854
<i>who would create such another
as I have been.</i>

1087
01:23:10,984 --> 01:23:13,362
<i>She is dead, who called me into being.</i>

1088
01:23:14,488 --> 01:23:17,059
<i>When I shall be no more,</i>

1089
01:23:17,124 --> 01:23:20,298
<i>the very remembrance of us both
will speedily vanish.</i>

1090
01:23:20,894 --> 01:23:24,137
<i>will no longer see the sun nor stars,</i>

1091
01:23:24,965 --> 01:23:27,309
<i>or feel the winds play upon my cheeks.</i>

1092
01:23:28,068 --> 01:23:30,912
<i>I shall ascend my funeral pile triumphantly</i>

1093
01:23:32,873 --> 01:23:35,581
<i>and exalt in the agony
of the torturing flames.</i>

1094
01:23:37,711 --> 01:23:40,351
<i>The light of that conflagration
will fade away.</i>

1095
01:23:41,482 --> 01:23:44,486
<i>My ashes will be swept into the sea
by the winds.</i>

1096
01:23:45,552 --> 01:23:47,759
<i>My spirit will sleep in peace.</i>

1097
01:23:48,889 --> 01:23:52,632
<i>Or if it thinks, it will not surely think thus.</i>

1098
01:23:55,262 --> 01:23:56,468
<i>Farewell.</i>

1099
01:24:44,478 --> 01:24:49,450
lam Adam!

